{{zh-forms|[[知]][[之]][[为]][[知]][[之]]，[[不]][[知]][[为]][[不]][[知]]|[[知之為知之，不知為不知]]}}
==Chinese==
===Mandarin===
[[Pinyin]]: zhī zhī wéi zhī zhī, bù zhī wéi bù zhī
===Etymology===
From the ''[[w:Analects of Confucius|Analects of Confucius]]''
===Proverb===
# You either know it or you don't (don't pretend to know it if you don't).
